high_descs: Turn around and veer to the rightmost sink.
Open the left cabinet and take out the blue rag.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Place the rag on the counter behind the soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go right to face the sink on the right.
Open the cabinet on the left below the sink on the right and pick up the green cloth.
Move a bit to the right and face the sink on the right.
Put the cloth in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick up the cloth again.
Go left and turn to face the counter between the sinks.
Put the cloth down on the counter between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cloth on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward toward the door, then turn right to face the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink, to the left; take out the rag.
Turn around, step forward, then turn back around to face the sink.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Turn left, move forward, then turn right to face the counter between the sinks.
Put the rag on the counter between the sinks, behind the soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag on the counter.
